metadata.name: ERRKKRRKK | 1 of 1s, #1
metadata.description:
ERRKKRRKK 1 of 1s # 1

This is my first drawing in 4 years, and first of my 1 of 1s. I took an open ended break to explore other avenues of creativity like web dev and photography. 

While this digital painting was simply a spontaneous exploration, it was subconsciously inspired by Cinema4d renders and Stable Diffusion claymation renders which I was drawing while the GPUs were doing their matrix multiplication thing üßÆ‚úçÔ∏è
